Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一集的Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:04.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了迎接地區預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!開始撰寫新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:09.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而我卻被最近接觸的遊戲吸引…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請不要告訴其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一旦這種事曝光的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:18.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學擔心我 表示要當學生會副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想為妳出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接受香音同學的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我坦白了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,與大家變得更加親近後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我終於將新曲完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:34.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開始舉行新生學生會的創立典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生會書記 櫻小路希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:41.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:46.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再來是會計 七草七海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:50.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是目前都沒想過的新人選呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了學校好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:56.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀學姐說也要讓音樂班以外的學生加入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:57.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不愧是學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可想當會計
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就多為社團出點力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生會長又離我更遙遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:06.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還沒放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:09.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生會副會長 澀谷香音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結丘女子高級中學學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將加入新成員繼續活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明年將是齊聚三個年級的重要年度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為此 本月將舉行校園開放日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:31.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我們一同宣傳本校的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,攜手打造令在場各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:36.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都能感到驕傲的美好學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來 奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掀起我們的旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爬上巔峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要拿下勝利!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:07.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不夠 還不夠 遠遠不夠!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不論何時我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越昨天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟能走到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然仍舊不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:18.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是要燃燒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想與你一同歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想了解尚未知曉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還會更加成長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想輕易放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在立刻 Start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向頂點前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還要更加 更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更加情緒高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去實現吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這瞬間 盡自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:52.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追尋夢想 盡自己全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:57.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為邂逅 給了我熱情的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是不可能的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也去實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會繼續相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 WE WILL!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:21.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像這個 這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#08 Chance Way)\N全都是Love Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是去年各校學園偶像使用過的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼還在講啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別擅自開燈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天亮了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Me too…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:42.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是 舞台確實很重要囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:42.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今年地區預賽突然變成了遠距大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因此在比去年多很多的參賽者中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們必須更吸引目光才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比去年多啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:56.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼具體的點子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可早就想到堇會問這種不經大腦的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:05.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,包下外苑球場計畫!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在球場中央搭建舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:20.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從360度各種角度來進行Liella!的直播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳之前不是才被回絕過一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CP值也是低到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題的 我們可是當地的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且還是優勝候補
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,身為學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可以還沒嘗試就先放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳能明白我的想法嗎…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要努力就一定能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,擁有不放棄的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才正是學園偶像!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對噠! 對噠!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,失敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被罵得好慘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們兩個意外地像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過這樣該選哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這種時候比起浪費錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更應該思考有效果的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有效果的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼好意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們好好想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏家是由觀眾進行人氣投票選出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:21.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,重點是如何引起觀眾的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,問題是方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比方說 投票給Liella!的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:36.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都能獲得在場成員的密藏照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:39.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後追加斗內money的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,竟然還…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都還沒說要幹嘛欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只能靠大家集思廣益找出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找出能充分傳達Liella! 結丘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:53.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以及我們幾個的象徵的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,象徵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,實在是想不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結丘的象徵嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如說到雪國的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就有下雪的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學校在海邊的話就是大海之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結丘附近也有很多知名景點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有很大條的路 還有店家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:22.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過那些能算是結丘的特色嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為太有名了 感覺無法代表結丘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:27.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是各社團的校園開放日企劃書喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這表示大家很重視這所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:39.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想大家都越來越喜歡學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像社這次打算做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全忘記了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然還是舉辦演唱會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我正打算提這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這次不辦演唱會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生會已經討論過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要讓我們專心準備地區預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不過多一場演唱會 可可完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我本來也是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那又怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小七海是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果辦演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會不會大家就都只注意Liella!了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟學園祭也辦過演唱會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,考慮整所學校的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這次就讓其他社團來炒熱氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或許才更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不辦演唱會唱歌的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(結丘女子 校園開放日)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:52.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,NEO彩虹章魚燒烤好囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 明明這麼圓的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得問題不在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:02.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,危機就是轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果不預測流行趨勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Money可是不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:15.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用上這杯為了章魚燒特製的高人氣冰沙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟章魚燒混合起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是彩虹章魚燒冰沙囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是要怎麼吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先將這根特製的吸管插入杯中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再一口氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喉嚨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直接燙到喉嚨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡看起沒問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子學妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以麻煩妳去幫忙音樂班的話劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,校園開放日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼多人來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"雖然學生人數少"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"但是更有團結力 是所好學校"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之前雜誌也這麼介紹了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逐漸成為妳媽媽理想中的學校了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,亞里亞? 妳今天有來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想給姐姐一個驚喜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再說我也得決定要念哪所學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣的話我可以帶妳參觀啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明年請務必考慮加入學園偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 小可可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,姐妹一起當學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是很熱血的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我甚至還沒決定要不要報考結丘耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有好多書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:47.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來香音妹妹對書有興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她這點很像我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放假時總是在讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然是姐妹但是興趣不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡原本是音樂學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼會想在這個地方建立學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:09.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會選這個地點的理由 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(章魚燒冰沙~)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啦 剩這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然冰沙根本就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是章魚燒的問題啦 章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不是 圓形是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟圓形沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,越講越複雜了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎樣都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意外地…不錯吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的假的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音樂學校的歷史…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了 要收拾才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經結束囉 給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,賣剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳在調查這座城市的歷史嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想說這所學校為什麼會建在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或許能成為決定舞台地點的線索…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:10:59.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那妳找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可惜還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(您有新訊息 悠奈)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,日團?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,舞台?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們想讓最信任的學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先看看我們的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可是我們的自信之作喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,日團大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這會爆紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就讓我先發到網路上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,信任關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 這就是國內首次公開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Sunny Passion今年的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,多麼美妙的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好想到現場看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是島上的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以我們為形象準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算我們能突破地區預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接著的東京大賽 還有後面的決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:59.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很高機率會選東京的大舞台來當會場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼一來 我們能在這座島上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以學園偶像身分站上舞台的機會就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為與這座島嶼共存
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有夥伴們的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們才能走到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們想跟這所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起讓島上變得更加熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望大家都能來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我們都辦場美好的演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們也得趕快找到才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天明明禮拜天 妳也很早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要去練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在那之前我想散步一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,散步?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,媽媽妳最喜歡這座城市的什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,5 6 7 8…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦 香音學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 學姐也在自行練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天我想找找選擇舞台的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:23.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了 小希奈子是今年才來這裡的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:24.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有空的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要跟我一起去街上逛逛?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟香音學姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要去要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟香音學姐一起逛街
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沾到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說回來 從早上就好多人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟是假日 所以更多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是常常在電視上看到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好多時髦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在拍戲耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到處都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論到哪都很熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都笑咪咪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子是在人煙稀少的地方長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以光是這樣就覺得很興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音學姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到處都很熱鬧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人潮聚集的城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐是不是找到什麼線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺…已經到這裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之後就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到Love Live結束前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音妳們就專心練習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這段期間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:00.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學生會的工作就交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們去年也有幫忙搭舞台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這讓我們很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但要是打進全國大賽的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,時間就會拉得很長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要麻煩妳們這麼久實在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們也想跟妳們分享喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以有什麼我們能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能幫忙的我們全都想做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了不留下任何遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要哭還太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都妳自己還不是哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟她是愛哭鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嘴上這麼說 堇學姐也在哭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是太謝謝妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來 1 2 3 4 5 6 7…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奇怪 數字怎樣都對不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從頭算看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼對不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來葉月同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一直都在做這麼辛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好好感受自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很擅長靜止不動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(Liella! 舞台會議!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在開始Liella!舞台會議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:29.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有任何點子的請儘管舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是舞台地點的候補名單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是七海同學她們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向校內同學做問卷調查的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟預料的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很多人選表參道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:49.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟這條路從100多年前就在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然比較引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我們去年就是在這裡唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,的確也能刻意選同個地點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但就缺乏衝擊力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一大難題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:06.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學校的大家是在這裡為我們搭建舞台的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:16.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家肯定是覺得這裡很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,表參道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才的名單裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有一個…還有一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既熱鬧 人潮又多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從很久以前就在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,串起大家想法 屬於我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跑太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我問妳怎樣就到底是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們…怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不管是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看到妳那樣突然衝出去都會很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我好像找到我們的舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,道路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的學校會建在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會不會是因為這裡是道路交會的場所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,道路…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為這裡是道路交會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,集結了人們的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是集結了每個人的夢想與希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,彼此連結的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我們才會選擇在這裡搭建舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:19.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人與人之間互相連結 產生連繫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結丘就是這樣的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這個道路交會的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們要獻上歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望Liella!的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結丘的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能與你產生交集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追逐夢想也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情喧鬧也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不在乎 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,試著傾聽自己內心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果不自由地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嘗試所有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就太可惜了! Jump吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Every time 都是祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,鼓起勇氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快點靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肆意喧鬧吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,往心跳的另一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備好就一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣不是很好嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:33.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,連上衣都想脫掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah! 盡情享受吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:41.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯! 我想更加了解你的事!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相遇之日正是 Chance Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,命運絕非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:53.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一同起舞吧 改變世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(全都變得Colorful)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:59.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,心情交織疊成 Chance Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,活力彼此連結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:08.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來做一件 最厲害的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:15.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放聲歌唱 一起歡笑玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,祭典開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:29.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,合而為一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們是結丘女子學園偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(結丘女子學園偶像)\N(Liella! 晉級東京大賽!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:12.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方 總是能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名為希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:20.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在閃爍著 閃爍耀眼光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟會走向何處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場場相遇之中 雖然又會迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請試著去享受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,覺得「似乎能做到卻做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後做到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會很開心 想著要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整顆心都像是要跳了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情歡笑 放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續走向遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界廣闊無邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然也有景色會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但熱情會始終如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越許多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要彈奏出什麼樣的悸動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改變未來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 為了勝利
